Josh Davis

Josh Davis

Josh Davis

Founder & CEO

Founder & CEO

Raised in East Dayton, OH with no shortcuts—just struggling parents

who let him dream big.


By 13, he was composing music for orchestras, writing jingles for Australian commercials as an Envato top-ranked author for over three consecutive months, and launching digital projects.


First in his family to graduate high school and go to college, he worked factory shifts while cold-calling prospects on breaks and teaching himself coding and design by night.


At 22, his dad passed at 43—making one thing clear: meaningful work can't wait.


Built Davis Strategic Media in 2018 (now Media That Sells), helping scrappy startups and established SMBs generate millions in lean revenue.


Mission: help you outgrow every excuse, outlast every competitor, and outshine every doubt while there's still time.

FAQ

Got any questions?
We've got answers.

Questions?
We've got answers.

What’s included in my Media That Sells subscription?

Our subscription offers a comprehensive, full-service marketing suite where we manage everything from strategy and creative to campaigns, tech, and analytics—all under one roof. This includes funnel planning, forecasting, and performance tracking, as well as design, copywriting, video production, and content amplification across multiple channels. We also handle campaign setup, ad buying, and optimization, with our Ad Engine reducing customer acquisition costs by up to 42%. On the tech side, we provide websites, CRM systems, email and social integrations, and workflow automation, with our Digital Chassis cutting tech debt by around 60%. Everything is delivered by one expert team through a straightforward monthly plan, with no long-term contract required.

How do I get started?

You can get started in just a few days with our simple 3-step onboarding process. First, activate by choosing a plan and sharing your current assets, like branding and accounts, to power up your infrastructure. Next, command by discussing your goals and priorities in a kickoff session, where we’ll tailor our approach to your objectives. Finally, deploy—our team moves quickly, executing with precision and delivering content and campaigns right away.

Who’s on my team and how do we collaborate?

You’ll have a dedicated account lead who coordinates a full team of specialists, including designers, copywriters, media buyers, developers, analysts, and more. We essentially become your in-house marketing department. We typically set up a shared workspace, like Slack, and hold regular check-ins to keep you informed and involved. Our team shares dashboards and deliverables in real time, so you can think of us as seamlessly integrated into your organization, collaborating non-stop from day one.

What technology and integrations do you manage?

We manage your entire marketing tech stack. This includes building and maintaining your website, apps, and backend systems at an enterprise scale, with our Digital Chassis reducing tech debt by around 60%. We also handle seamless integrations, connecting your CRM, analytics, ad platforms, email, e-commerce, and more via APIs and workflows. In short, all your marketing tools and data sources are synced and managed by us.

How do you leverage AI and automation?

We integrate AI and automation throughout our process. With Agentic AI, we deploy intelligent AI agents that strategize and execute autonomously, allowing us to scale efforts without increasing headcount. Additionally, every campaign includes automated touches like lead follow-ups, triggers, and personalization. Our Intuitive Automation has been proven to double inbound conversion velocity, ensuring that no leads slip through the cracks.

How fast will I see real progress with Media That Sells?

Our Launch Logic accelerates the ramp-up process by about 70%, so deliverables start coming in days instead of months. We eliminate bottlenecks and get campaigns live right away, ensuring that milestones are achieved quickly and predictably.

How do you ensure predictable scope and outcomes?

We work on a fixed monthly plan with clearly defined deliverables—no hidden fees or surprise add-ons. Our MRR guarantee ensures "zero scope creep": we outline exactly what's included in each cycle and stick to the plan. If we miss an agreed target, it's on us. This flat-fee, no-contract model ensures your outcomes stay rock-solid.

How does the Venture Studio partnership work?

We go beyond the typical vendor-client relationship and become your growth partner, with skin in the game. This means we co-invest our time—and sometimes capital—into new ventures. We co-invest, co-build, and co-scale bold ideas alongside you. MediaThatSells is a "venture suite fusing marketing mastery with agentic AI," allowing us to apply our full-stack resources and intelligence to scale your business as if it were our own.

We also handle seamless integrations, connecting your CRM, analytics, ad platforms, email, e-commerce, and more via APIs and workflows. In short, all your marketing tools and data sources are synced and managed by us.

How do you leverage AI and automation?

We integrate AI and automation throughout our process. With Agentic AI, we deploy intelligent AI agents that strategize and execute autonomously, allowing us to scale efforts without increasing headcount. Additionally, every campaign includes automated touches like lead follow-ups, triggers, and personalization. Our Intuitive Automation has been proven to double inbound conversion velocity, ensuring that no leads slip through the cracks.

How fast will I see real progress with Media That Sells?

Our Launch Logic accelerates the ramp-up process by about 70%, so deliverables start coming in days instead of months. We eliminate bottlenecks and get campaigns live right away, ensuring that milestones are achieved quickly and predictably.

How do you ensure predictable scope and outcomes?

We work on a fixed monthly plan with clearly defined deliverables—no hidden fees or surprise add-ons. Our MRR guarantee ensures "zero scope creep": we outline exactly what's included in each cycle and stick to the plan. If we miss an agreed target, it's on us. This flat-fee, no-contract model ensures your outcomes stay rock-solid.

How does the Venture Studio partnership work?

We go beyond the typical vendor-client relationship and become your growth partner, with skin in the game. This means we co-invest our time—and sometimes capital—into new ventures. We co-invest, co-build, and co-scale bold ideas alongside you. MediaThatSells is a "venture suite fusing marketing mastery with agentic AI," allowing us to apply our full-stack resources and intelligence to scale your business as if it were our own.
